/* Title: googleDrive */

onen google drive and Right click the image you want to share and click Share...

Click Advanced and change the Who can access option to anyone with the link or Nxglabs(in same oraganization)

Copy the link to share and you will have something like this : https://drive.google.com/file/d/FILE_ID/view?usp=sharing

Copy the FILE_ID to make a link like this: https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=FILE_ID

Insert image in Markdown as ususal using the link from above step. For example: markdownImageEx
